Dialogs.Dialog: Should we have our lunch here？ It looks comfy.
We can eat lunch here, right？
Japanese food takes a lot of time and effort.
You did your best, right？ Thank you. Bon appetit！
It's like the taste of my mother's cooking, made by your girlfriend. Try it.
Yes！ I knew it's Japanese style. Bon appetit！
How's it？ I hope I've recreated the taste of a Western restaurant.
It has my favorite dishes. Bon appetit！
It's pretty cute, isn't it？ For the... well, you will have to judge for yourself.
This Western-style bento looks delicious. Bon appetit！
It looks weird, but the taste should be Chinese in its own way... probably.
Nice, that's a generous portion！ Bon appetit.
Here, it's the Rinko's full bento experience.
Oooh, that's some mighty fine Chinese！ Bon appetit.
Yes, it looks pretty good, doesn't it？ Hehe, I'm proud of myself.
Here's Rinko's special bento. You're a lucky guy, really.
Yes, I know. Delicious！ Bon appetit.
Hey, do you want me... to feed you？
Hmm, well, today's special. Come on, open wide.
Don't be shy, open your mouth. Say "Ah"！
I see, that's a waste of time.
...Why are you taking it seriously？ Idiot.
Hey... Rinko would like to have some. You know what I mean.
I guess it can't be helped
Hehe... this kind of things makes us look like lovers.
It's okay. Come on, hurry it up！ "ah"...
It was good！ Five-star class. Thanks for the food.
Hah, it was delicious. Maybe even good enough to serve in a restaurant. Thanks for the food.
Really？ It's worth making if you're that happy.
It was a feast. Thank you.
Phew... It was the taste of my first experience.
That' s kind of a bemused impression...
(Your cooking skills are rough around the edges, ▲小早川＊▲.)
(Your cooking skills seem to be improving, ▲小早川＊▲.)
(Your cooking skills have improved so much this time, ▲小早川＊▲.)
(Your cooking skills are at a level that make me proud, ▲小早川＊▲.)
(Your cooking skill can't be considered the likes of an amateur anymore, ▲小早川＊▲.)
(Your cooking skills are at a level where you can start teaching people, ▲小早川＊▲.)
(Your cooking skills are on par with a top chef, ▲小早川＊▲.)
(Your cooking skills are as good as a three star restaurant, ▲小早川＊▲.)
(Your cooking skills are at the level of the best in the world, ▲小早川＊▲.)
(Your cooking skills are the best in human history, ▲小早川＊▲！)
Hey, what would you like next？ I might make it for you if I feel like it.
I'm in the mood for Japanese food
I'd really like to try ▲料理ジャンル▲.
That's Rinko's specialty. Leave it to me.
I see. Well, I'll keep that in mind.
So you want that. I'm not too confident.
Hmmm... I'll think about it, but don't get your hopes up.
Hmm, I hope it turns out good.
It's your first time here. Anyway, let's go in.
You already know most of the menu here.
Do you like this restaurant so much？ ...Well, if it's okay with you, it's fine.
I'm starving, so everything looks delicious. I'm sure it's just my imagination.
Hmm, I wonder what I should try.
I think I'll try ▲生成選択肢１▲. What do you want to eat, ▲小早川＊▲？
What, you want Rinko to decide？ Well... how about this one？
Sounds good. Then I'll have ▲生成選択肢１▲.
▲生成選択肢２▲？ Sounds good. I'll call the waiter then.
Hmm？ What's wrong with my hair？
I want your hair the way it was when we met
Hmm... no, it was nothing after all.
Why don't you wear your hair the way it was when we met？
I see, I wonder from what kind of mindset that comes from. Well, I'll think about it.
What, feeling nostalgic？ But, you know, you can't rush into things. Wait for it.
Yeah, I'll leave it to you.
I thought it might be a good idea to change your hair.
Hmmm, great, Rinko was just thinking about changing her hair too. Well, let me know how you like it.
I see... I would have liked to have seen something different.
I like your hair the way it is now. I'd like to keep it that way.
Hmm, you're so honest. Hehe, Rinko likes her hair too.
Hmm... until Rinko gets tired of it.
Length？ Do you care about it？
Why don't you grow it longer？
Then you're saying it's fine the way it is.
So you prefer it that way. Okay, I'll think about it.
Yes, it would definitely look good on you.
I'll keep it in the back of my mind... Leave it there.
Hey, the accessory you're wearing today...
I thought that hair accessory was a nice touch.
I thought those earrings looked good on you.
That necklace looks great on you.
That arm thing looks good on you.
I like that ring. It looks good on you.
I was thinking those glasses look good on you.
Hmm... hehe, I'll keep it on for a while.
I thought that hair accessory didn't look very good on you.
Those earrings don't look good on you...
That necklace doesn't look good on you.
That thing on your arm... doesn't look good on you.
I don't think that kind of glasses look good on you ▲小早川＊▲.
I see. Then I won't do it again...
I'm sorry. But you should try other things.
How do you choose the clothes you use, ▲小早川＊▲？
How, you ask... I just pick them normally.
Why don't you pick a genre？
Why don't you choose it by shape？
How about you choose by shape？
You mean silhouettes？ Hmmm, so what kind？
How about a skirt？ Like a normal girl.
I'd like to see you using a one piece.
I like the pants style. They say it makes you look slender.
I think... it'll be more refreshing... to be a little more exposed.
That's the kind of thing I like. I'm sure your sweet girlfriend will respond to your request.
Hmm... So, in short, you don't like the current Rinko.
It would be interesting to try to choose by color.
I think I like bright cold colors. They're refreshing.
I like calm, warm colors. I like the image of being together and feeling at ease.
A calm, cold color would be nice, don't you think？ It would look good on you ▲小早川＊▲.
If you insist so much, I guess it can't be helped. It's also my duty to respond to the needs of my boyfriend.
Well, I think it needs to be the cute type.
I quite like casual fashion for girls.
Men, you know, they want their girlfriends to be neat and tidy.
Well, yeah. I guess it's just how it is now.
Hmm, so that's what you think. Well, I'll give it a try.
That being said, Rinko likes that kind of thing.
Hey, why don't you change the way you call me？
Depends on what you want. How do you want to be called？
That's fine, I'll leave it like that. I'm used to it.
How do you like to call me ▲新主人公▲？
How do you like to call me ▲新主人公▲？
...Are you happy with it？ If it's okay with you, it's fine.
I'd like you to call me ▲新主人公▲...
Surprisingly, it's not so bad. I might like it a lot.
Don't you think it'll be good to call me ▲新主人公▲？
It's true. Rinko likes this way of calling you.
Hmm, I'm thinking of changing the way I call you ▲小早川＊▲.
Nope. Rinko is fine like that.
It would be nice to call you ▲生成選択肢５▲.
...Are you serious？ If so, I question your sense of humor.
How about I call you ▲生成選択肢５▲？
Wouldn't be better to call you ▲生成選択肢５▲？
Heh. It's okay, I can't help it.
How about I call you ▲生成選択肢５▲？
All right. That's pretty good too.
What do you think Rinko's hair should look like？ Think about it with me.
I think it's fine the way it is
Ah, I see... It's just not worth the hassle.
I really like things the way they are.
What kind of mood do you want？
Then, I think for you, ▲小早川＊▲...
How about we pick one from here？
Hmmm... so this is the way to go. So, which one？
I see. So which of these is the best one？
Around here, don't think it looks good.
Yes, they look good... But which is the best？
Which one would you like to see...
I wonder if it would look good on Rinko.
Hmm, I wonder if it's okay.
Rinko wonders if this is right...
What do you think about this hair length？
Isn't Rinko's current hair not long enough？
Yeah, that's good. This is the one！
It definitely looks good on you.
This？ Hmm... well, I guess it's fine.
Just make sure you pick the right one for my hair, okay？
Make sure it looks good on Rinko, okay？ Do you understand？
And while you're at it, think about the color.
Do not try to make a fool of me, okay？
Yeah, that sounds good. I think it's not difficult to keep it.
I see. I think I have a general idea of what you like.
Thank you for your patience. Please take your time.
This is good！ It's delicious, try it.
That one looks delicious. Can I have some？
It was a feast. How was it？
Yup. Better than I thought, I was honestly surprised. Maybe I could live here.
Yeah, it was pretty good. Let's come back.
I don't think it's that good...
(Not good... What was wrong with it？)
Ah, geez. I'm so full. I'm very satisfied.
The taste and quantity are just right.
The taste was good, but the volume was a little too much.
...I'm full. It tasted a bit bland, but I ended up eating it.
I hope my stomach is full. I can't praise the taste, though.
The taste is no good, and they are stingy with the quantity...
It's nice and relaxing. Let's come back again.
I'm afraid I couldn't relax a bit in this place. Too bad.
I like the tableware and the interior design.
There's no atmosphere in this shop.
I hear this place's popular now.
Hmm, well, the taste depends on the person？
Ah... I guess I screwed up.
It had a good reputation. It was delicious.
I think... it might have disappointed me.
